權既好影響同壞影響係同一nature可以抵消<br />\n而抵消後壞影響依然大無限倍<br />\n咁個&quot;好處&quot;in a sense其實係人血饅頭<br />\n巨體咁講 極權殺左好多人 有機會下個就係你 亦會剝奪你其他自由<br />\n咁樣禁止公眾地方用喇叭比較起黎就太微不足度<br />\n因為你都可能俾人拉左 就算條街靚哂都唔關你事<br />\n<br />\n相反有啲處境好影響同壞影響唔係同一nature<br />\n例如走堂雖然整體係壞多過好<br />\n但係走左堂多左時間休息 呢樣野同個grade差左係兩樣nature唔同既事<br />\n咁就可以算係好處"},{"pid":"70980321d75c2939ec589dd0f38529370c530c53","tid":2304852,"uid":233905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37da4643339dd603a0b6518d9ac2e071c5dabe6a","tid":2304852,"uid":92859,"like":1276,"dislike":19,"score":1257,"citedBy":18,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T07:09:22.000Z","msg":"強權有強權嘅好處<br />\n民主有民主嘅壞處<br />\n<br />\n香港政府完美集結哂強權同民主嘅壞處<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T13:34:21.000Z","msg":"民主都可以處理呢啲嘢㗎<br />\n咪由立法機關草擬返法例囉<br />\n獨裁只有壞處冇好處"},{"pid":"c68d67aeff03d247ff1c896828295d55b845e97e","tid":2304852,"uid":372210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T13:35:08.000Z","msg":"支持，幾時喺香港實行。"},{"pid":"e0ff840ee628110b97ca02ed1177cbfc03444eeb","tid":2304852,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35294dda18e7adc61fe721ae820234a41fa7e1ce","tid":2304852,"uid":91017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ae3cfc0690eeab93f2d77c21772abef8a1bcf92","tid":2304852,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2a44c7eb58aebff0cbb0df02075cf91c1f3a2cc","tid":2304852,"uid":91017,"like":77,"dislike":2,"score":75,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T07:14:25.000Z","msg":"吊, 係班死老野, 大媽唔識用藍牙<br />\n應該出返d有耳插既機種"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T10:18:38.000Z","msg":"有線耳筒最平幾蚊條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T10:56:22.000Z","msg":"宜家好多機冇左插"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T13:43:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.fortress.com.hk/medias/SIDO-S229-Type-C-to-